Mixed Model

There is need to scale POG before building the model.

days <- scale(pro$POG)
pro$days1 <- days[,1]

Building model1 without using Group

model1 <- lmer(log(SHLA.G.levels)~ days1 + I(days1^2) + 
                I(days1^3)+ (1|Enrid), data = pro, REML = F)
summary(model1)
